snippet.title: D.C. BEYOND
snippet.description: Fan of dc all my life.supported zack snyder on fbook now full time here sharing my thoughts with you. I may not say what you believe but maybe you can change that. We are all fans of DC an want it to succeed. So please share my hopes my fears. All I ask is that you share my videos for I hardly tag my videos for I believe in word of mouth. If you like this channel please check out. Your movie review and the inner mind
